Extended resection of non-small cell lung cancer invading the left atrium, is it 
worth the risk?

Galvaing G(1), Chadeyras JB(2), Merle P(3), Tardy MM(2), Naamee A(2), Bailly 
P(2), Filaire M(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Thoracic Surgery, Jean Perrin Comprehensive Cancer Center, 58 
rue Montalembert, 63000 Clermont-Ferrand, France. geraud.galvaing@cjp.fr.
(2)Department of Thoracic Surgery, Jean Perrin Comprehensive Cancer Center, 
